# Q35 CoCo (SEV-SNP) + single GPU: x86_64, single NUMA node, 17 vCPUs
# Source: production kata-containers log, July 2026 (AMD EPYC host, H100 80GB GPU)
# Binary: qemu-system-x86_64-snp-experimental
# host-data is a synthetic placeholder, not production-captured material.
#
# Platform scope: sev-snp-guest object + machine line + NUMA RAM backend +
#   NUMA node + pxb-pcie + pcie-root-port + per-device iommufd + vfio-pci.
# NOT included here (legacy generator): -name, -uuid, -cpu, -m, -smp,
#   pcie-root-port+pcie-pci-bridge for legacy device compat, virtio devices,
#   -netdev, -kernel, -append, -bios (AMDSEV.fd), -rtc, -pidfile, etc.
#
# HostTopology: 1 socket, cpus 0-16, host-node 1
# Memory: 57344M, single NUMA node, memory-backend-ram with host-nodes=1,policy=bind
#   (NOT file-backed; CoCo uses memory-backend-ram for NUMA pinning)
# GPU: 0000:e1:00.0 (NVIDIA H100 80GB, 0x10de:0x2321)
#   pxb-pcie bus_nr=32, chassis=10 (different from Grace 1-indexed formula)
#   vfio-pci (NOT vfio-pci-nohotplug — x86 CoCo uses standard vfio-pci)
#   x-pci-vendor-id/x-pci-device-id required for CoCo measured boot attestation
#   iommufd is PER-DEVICE (not shared iommufd0): id=iommufdvfio-<device-uuid>
#   No arm-smmuv3: x86 uses global AMD/Intel IOMMU, not per-bus SMMU
# BIOS: /opt/kata/share/ovmf/AMDSEV.fd (AMD-specific OVMF, not generic OVMF.fd)
#
# New Platform fields required (Phase 3):
#   Objects::protection: Option<ProtectionDevice>  (sev-snp-guest or tdx-guest)
#   Q35::kernel_irqchip: String  ("split" for CoCo, "on" for plain Q35, absent otherwise)
#   Q35::confidential_guest_support: Option<String>  (references protection object id)
#   MemoryBackend::Ram { host_nodes: Option<u32>, policy: Option<String> }
#   PciRootComplex::iommufd: Option<IommufdRef>  (per-device iommufd, not shared)
#   VfioDevice::vendor_id / device_id overrides  (required for CoCo attestation)
-object
sev-snp-guest,id=snp,cbitpos=51,reduced-phys-bits=1,kernel-hashes=on,policy=196608,host-data=S0FUQS1TWU5USEVUSUMtSE9TVC1EQVRBLTAwMDAwMDA=
-machine
q35,accel=kvm,kernel_irqchip=split,confidential-guest-support=snp
-object
memory-backend-ram,id=numa-mem0,size=57344M,host-nodes=1,policy=bind
-numa
node,nodeid=0,memdev=numa-mem0,cpus=0-16
-device
pxb-pcie,id=pxb-numa0,bus=pcie.0,bus_nr=32,numa_node=0
-device
pcie-root-port,id=rp-numa0-0,bus=pxb-numa0,chassis=10,slot=0,multifunction=off
-object
iommufd,id=iommufdvfio-ab57592a4d2482201
-device
vfio-pci,host=0000:e1:00.0,id=vfio-ab57592a4d2482201,x-pci-vendor-id=0x10de,x-pci-device-id=0x2321,bus=rp-numa0-0,iommufd=iommufdvfio-ab57592a4d2482201
